Kisii Senator Chris Obure has intensified campaigns for President Uhuru Kenyatta&rsquo;s reelection. Addressing teachers at Sameta Boys High School on Saturday, he said, &ldquo;I am urging you to support Jubilee because it has your best interest at heart. I want to assure you that as leaders we are going to ensure that money is allocated to hike your salaries as agreed in the CBA.&rdquo;